BETA TESTING OFFER  (AND DISCOUNT COUPON)

I need as many eyes as possible looking at this site for me. You will
really be doing me a favor, as I'm bleary eyed and just can't finish it
up without some extra sets of eyes. (I've been working on this for six
months now - and 80 to 90 hours a week for the last month. I'm ready to
drop!)  But the site is still rough, even with all that work. It just
takes forever to manually sift through hundreds of thousands of entries
looking for errors, so there are lots that weren't found yet.

So what I'm asking is this. Put the site through its paces. You can even
place an "order."  As long as you do it before 3 AM Monday morning (on
the new website, not busdepot.com), it will not be processed, since we
are only testing.  Look for anything and everything, and send me a list
of whatever you find.  Hopefully, a long list!   Email it to me directly
-   ron(-at-)busdepot.com  - with BETA included in the subject header.

If you send me a legitimate list of problems/errors/issues (there are
plenty to find!), I'll reciprocate by sending you a coupon code for 10%
off a Bus Depot order (good for a limited timeframe). That's double the
normal listmember discount. (Same terms as normal listmember discount
will apply.)  If you want, while you're testing the site, you can even
put together an order for your 10% discount, save it under your account
using the Want List feature until the site goes live, and then later
retrieve it and apply the coupon.  (Note: See Want List bug below.)

The types of problems that I'd like to know about include (but are not
limited to):

1) Graphics or cosmetic flaws:  i.e. a line break in the text that
shouldn't be there, causing one word to sit off by itself, or any other
cosmetic flaws.  Since many of you have different web browsers, the site
may look slightly different for you than for me.

2) Part data errors:
- Part application errors (i.e. when you click on the part, the details
show that it doesn't fit the VW model it is listed under)
- Part descriptions that are wrong, don't make sense, missing, etc.
- Duplicate parts (i.e. the same part listed twice under different part
numbers, perhaps even at different prices)
- Please look over the CAR listings too. This is particularly important
since I haven't looked at them much myself. If you have a VW car, browse
for parts for it and tell me what you think/find.

3)  Picture errors:  i.e. the wrong picture, a picture that still says
"click back on your browser" from the old busdepot site, etc.

4)  Bugs in the way the features work, navigation, etc. Coupon code
(i.e. PROJECT800), want list, etc. (Exactly what were you doing that
made the bug show up?)

5) General comments and suggestions. Be brutally honest. I really want
to know.

KNOWN BUGS: (hopefully fixed sometime on the weekend):
I) WANT LIST:  for the time being you MUST LOG-OUT (using the "my
account" screen) before you exit your browser, or the want list will not
be saved.
2) Emailed order-confirmation letter needs some work. 
3) Coupon code not working reliably???
